manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: 360° Rotating Aluminum Alloy Wall Mount Folding Support for Amazon Echo Show 15 Smart Display. Portable stretch design. Just the right amount of stretch damping for a smooth and comfortable feel.

Details Make Perfect ! Securely Get Your Echo Show 15 Monitor Mounted ! 3-axis and 3-arm design. Extendable rocker arm structure, strong bearing capacity, improve firmness and stability, maximum bearing capacity of 33 pounds, the wall monitor mount is crafted with heavy-duty materials and a sleek finish to blend in perfectly with any decor.

This wall mount for echo show 15 tilts, rotates, and swivels for the perfect angle to watch your favorite, shows, movies, and sports and allows you to create an ergonomic position to avoid unnecessary neck and back strain.

Comes with detailed instruction, all necessary hardware in pre-labeled bags, helps you finish the installation quickly and easily.

The front bracket can be rotated 360° up and down, left and right, to achieve a richer viewing experience. This full motion TV wall mount allows you to maximize space by mounting your TV in a corner by adjusting the mount's articulating arms.
